OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy outbreaks of rain in the
OL,6,Fwest today, gradually moving east.
OL,7,FSunny spells elsewhere and feeling hot
OL,8,Fand humid again in eastern England. A
OL,9,Ffresher feel elsewhere with a gentle
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in northwest Scotland
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain. Drier
OL,14,Felsewhere with clear spells. A much
OL,15,Ffresher night compared to recent days
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FDry with sunny spells for
OL,18,Fmany. Scattered showers are possible
OL,19,Facross the north. Temperatures around
OL,20,Fthe seasonal average for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
